To predict what exactly is going to be in the second half of the year is quite tough. But what we do see is as we prepare for some of these trials, example, the combat arms trial that's on in Florida right now with the MDL, as well as some of the other cases that will start picking up in PFAS, we expect that our legal fees -- or legal cost to prepare for these trials will go up during the second half of this year.

Deane Dray -- RBC Capital Markets -- Analyst

